>> At your DNS provider, create records such as:
>> Type Name Target
>> A ai VPS IP
>> A hermes VPS IP
>> A n8n VPS IP
>> A grafana VPS IP
>> A api VPS IP
>>
>> If you use Cloudflare, leave the proxy enabled unless a specific service
>> requires direct access.
