>> Create:
>> logs/
>>
>> traefik/
>>
>> docker/
>>
>> system/
>>
>>
>> Logs are invaluable when diagnosing:
>> certificate failures
>> DNS issues
>> container crashes
>> routing problems
>> Rotate logs regularly so they don't consume excessive disk space.
